DROP TABLE Diary IF EXISTS; CREATE TABLE Diary (id INT PRIMARY KEY AUTO_INCREMENT NOT NULL, date date NOT NULL, user_id varchar(12) NOT NULL, note varchar(140), photo varchar(100) NOT NULL,
